re <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ), so you don't have to start researching multiples of each pet every time to make sure you have the needed components.<br>
<br>
There was a time when I thought that doing the practice research was gonna be the way to go, but it turned out to be WAY more hassle than it was worth to me. I kept the concordance as a light 6 slot bag, and nowadays I just shell out the plat to use my practice points every level...<br>
<br>
Pretty much all of the utility summons are available at the Library in Erudin (top floor, the vendor wanders around, so be patient), The Library Mechamagia in Ak'Anon (2 vendors in a room to the left as you enter the library) or Neriak (never been there, not into getting killed! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
